<br>
Since the IPR in this last patch, I'm reallocating my bow MA's IP and dumping her bow completely.  It's just not worth it compared to fists -- or the new Claws.<br>
<br>
If you want to blow some IP, get a Claw instead of a bow :-)<br>
<br>
